Name: Misfit
About the game: Misfit is a third person shooter, in which you battle over objectives, take down other players, fight waves of enemies, and survive until the portal opens for you to escape. Features: -fluid third person gameplay -A multiplayer game you've never experienced before -Wide variety of abilities such as Super Speed, Mega Jump, Grenade Launcher, and Giant Mech Armour -Multiple maps to choose from, including ancient deserts, modern cities and medieval castles
